{"tid":2160842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鍾庭耀：議員「杯葛臨立會」民調，周二開始，周五公布","createTime":"2020-08-17T08:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T13:48:04.000Z","uid":134071,"like":140,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"b1baff3ae7508e9fd1eb540a7d9662a46fd97c64","tid":2160842,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:28:34.000Z","msg":"撰文: 記者林勵 | 發佈日期: 17.08.20<br />\n<br />\n民主派就是否立法會去留問題未定案，對民意走勢亦有不同判斷。香港民意研究所將會在周二起進行民意調查，研究所總監鍾庭耀接受眾新聞查詢時說，自稱民主派當然應該非常尊重民意，又說最好的方法是先民調再投票，「也是一種政治判斷和承擔」。<br />\n<br />\n民調目前預計在周二開始，周五公布。除朱凱迪支持民主派以公投或民調作決定外，其他民主派目前仍未表態是否跟隨民調決定去留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/32984/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%BB%B6%E4%BB%BB-%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-32984/%E3%80%90%E5%BB%B6%E4%BB%BBvs%E7%B8%BD%E8%BE%AD%E3%80%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF%E5%95%8F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%8E%BB%E7%95%99-%E9%8D%BE%E5%BA%AD%E8%80%80%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%88%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF%E5%86%8D%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E6%98%AF%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%89%BF%E6%93%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F32984%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-32984%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BB%25BBvs%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%2595%258F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258E%25BB%25E7%2595%2599-%25E9%258D%25BE%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E8%2580%2580%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2585%2588%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%2589%25BF%25E6%2593%2594&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=36c4883f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: