,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:58:20.000Z","msg":"最佳做法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f464e2a8edb9bb6b84b842dceb27c7486569e58","tid":2160842,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"如果可以主動做問卷更好"},{"pid":"1aa41ca6290874a2077e6b6b12bc48b76ae93bf4","tid":2160842,"uid":188035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1baff3ae7508e9fd1eb540a7d9662a46fd97c64","tid":2160842,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:28:34.000Z","msg":"撰文: 記者林勵 | 發佈日期: 17.08.20<br />\n<br />\n民主派就是否立法會去留問題未定案，對民意走勢亦有不同判斷。香港民意研究所將會在周二起進行民意調查，研究所總監鍾庭耀接受眾新聞查詢時說，自稱民主派當然應該非常尊重民意，又說最好的方法是先民調再投票，「也是一種政治判斷和承擔」。<br />\n<br />\n民調目前預計在周二開始，周五公布。除朱凱迪支持民主派以公投或民調作決定外，其他民主派目前仍未表態是否跟隨民調決定去留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/32984/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%BB%B6%E4%BB%BB-%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-32984/%E3%80%90%E5%BB%B6%E4%BB%BBvs%E7%B8%BD%E8%BE%AD%E3%80%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF%E5%95%8F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%8E%BB%E7%95%99-%E9%8D%BE%E5%BA%AD%E8%80%80%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%88%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF%E5%86%8D%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E6%98%AF%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%89%BF%E6%93%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F32984%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-32984%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BB%25BBvs%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%2595%258F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258E%25BB%25E7%2595%2599-%25E9%258D%25BE%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E8%2580%2580%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2585%2588%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%2589%25BF%25E6%2593%2594&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=36c4883f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/32984/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%BB%B6%E4%BB%BB-%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-32984/%E3%80%90%E5%BB%B6%E4%BB%BBvs%E7%B8%BD%E8%BE%AD%E3%80%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF%E5%95%8F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%8E%BB%E7%95%99-%E9%8D%BE%E5%BA%AD%E8%80%80%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%88%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF%E5%86%8D%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E6%98%AF%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%89%BF%E6%93%94</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:05:31.000Z","msg":"總辭啦"},{"pid":"d1e166950fdd17f742824ae8825a1bbd9e0d5f00","tid":2160842,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:06:18.000Z","msg":"點投？"},{"pid":"d046f4a51b5bafbbe3024229e61c3b5a8d723c98","tid":2160842,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:07:19.000Z","msg":"其實一直以黎， 網上問卷點防人用bot洗結果？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f7adc177f765053404be76d3d53673c80632cc","tid":2160842,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1e166950fdd17f742824ae8825a1bbd9e0d5f00","tid":2160842,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:06:18.000Z","msg":"點投？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:07:39.000Z","msg":"<em>有別於全港抽樣的特首民望民調，香港民研今次民調屬「我們香港人」計劃下，向意見群組發出問卷。副行政總監鍾劍華向眾新聞解釋，他們在大約10萬人的群組中發放網上問卷，每次大約收回1萬份回覆，雖然不屬於全港性抽樣，但同樣會加權作為參考。他表示，有關做法偏差會較全港性抽樣較大，「所以是一個indicative survey（參考性調查），而不是conclusive survey（決定性調查）」。他表示，同樣意見群組調查方法亦見諸外國選舉及初選，但調查未必直接決定民主派議員的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n對於部分民主派私下質疑民調方式，鍾劍華強調，明白民主派面對很大壓力，不想因為民調而騎虎難下，但作為民調機構無法考慮個別派別盤算，正如「特首都未必鐘意我哋特首民望調查，但我哋唔會因此唔做」。</em>"},{"pid":"f0574393bf4afce4989be10dab3a51c6acfc6b0d","tid":2160842,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:08:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"726c872278c3b84fa213cf2f588362dca071f268","tid":2160842,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9529ed1c68955a827dc83cedc6928f0cf3fff459","tid":2160842,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6ea742c4348aa4c318ce9dca55242e789971fb35","tid":2160842,"uid":20870,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8175e1f5763253155c3ab92c1b2a574b3456a9ca","tid":2160842,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:34:05.000Z","msg":"袋多百幾萬落袋，理得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依你咁講 還掂袋左 咩唔做就得啦 仲整咩民調用錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:55:02.000Z","msg":"講緊販民班人唔係鍾庭耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:10:41.000Z","msg":"條友真係唔識.jpg"},{"pid":"4ffc8b260967949464ce7805ac0f1ffa1c1cad93","tid":2160842,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8824f793c32839a10dc0022386a0b7df271e66bf","tid":2160842,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edf285e6237343acaa80d0a3ba2046d555e2e144","tid":2160842,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3206b2a7c81f5f3d2460a8f29fb1276b61414a8d","tid":2160842,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:47:59.000Z","msg":"有個明確指標去定留還好...<br />\n到時50/50或者40/60, 就最麻煩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:52:09.000Z","msg":"好難大比數，<br />\n唔計結果，淨係睇過程：討論平台、機會不足、雙方宣傳不足難令受訪者有理性決定、隨機抽樣方法、sample size全部都會令呢個民調唔完整，<br />\n一定公投最公平"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:56:29.000Z","msg":"其實